-- DirecTV quarterly profit and revenue rise
-- 
-- Wed May 9, 2007 7:46am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/09/us-directv-results-idUSWEN787920070509

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - DirecTV Group Inc DTV.N on Wednesday posted higher first quarter profit and revenue as it added new satellite television subscribers. 

 Its profit rose to $336 million, or 27 cents per share from $235 million, or 17 cents a share in the year-ago quarter. Revenue rose to $3.91 billion from $3.39 billion. DirecTV added 235,000 U.S. customers in the quarter.